content: azep-ninja: Merged three significant PRs this week, including a new token security analysis plugin (#2391, +193k/-15k lines), and enhancements to both Telegram (#2338, +54k/-4k lines) and Discord (#2335, +65k/-9k lines) autonomous agents.
